name: Everything-old
tagline: Contains older source of things that probably dont work anymore.
body:
### Welcome
Since 2003 (probably even before), I have been learning the various technologies available. I have butched code across as many platforms as I have languages. Here is what I consider is a bunchh of "old stuff" that have no interest in continuing developing. It is largely obsolete, in terms of language, and, in most cases, are examples of what not to do. 

### Summary of Items
I will endeavor to publish a detailed description of each sub directory in this repository. All new development will like be given its own repository. 

##Copyright 2015 by Mack Gammeter
